imdb.plot outline: Writing English Assessments can be hard. Annabelle Williams decides to type hers about love. She gets specific about what love means to her as a single, seventeen year old year twelve student and it all boils down to one man: Justin Bieber. Confronting her past, she battles the competition almost without a single thought of Selena. The question is, will she win Justin Bieber's heart?
